That's 10 meters away.

00:03:01.700 --> 00:03:03.520
But you get the general idea.

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:05.350
Now let's keep going.

00:03:05.350 --> 00:03:08.760
Let's think about the crest
that both of these guys

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:11.130
emitted 2 seconds ago.

00:03:11.130 --> 00:03:13.700
This guy's been stationary
the whole time.

00:03:13.700 --> 00:03:17.430
If he emitted it 2 seconds
ago, it's traveling at 10

00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:18.860
meters per second.

